WEBVTT

00:01.269 --> 00:06.825
A singular new design, a re-engineered chip and 5G.

00:07.598 --> 00:09.656
This is iPhone 12 Pro.

00:10.492 --> 00:13.898
A new and improved Pro camera system makes the 12 Pro...

00:14.179 --> 00:15.772
...the photographer's iPhone.

00:16.455 --> 00:20.816
The larger iPhone 12 Pro Max takes these innovations even further.

00:22.001 --> 00:25.382
Its bigger sensor dramatically increases the detail captured...

00:25.514 --> 00:28.931
...and helps improve low-light performance by 87 percent.

00:30.585 --> 00:33.570
An integral part of this year's design is Magsafe,...

00:34.217 --> 00:38.161
...an intelligent system of magnets that connect accessories in a whole new way.

00:42.017 --> 00:47.785
All this and more make iPhone 12 Pro the most powerful iPhone ever.

